title: Muscle Cars Meet Formula 1 - /DRIVE American Roadtrip Trailer
description: The boys take a traditional American road trip in three muscle cars to Former F1 circuit Watkins Glen. Chris Harris in the new Ford Mustang, Matt Farah in the Camaro Z28, and Mike Spinelli in the Charger Hellcat.
tags: Ford Mustang, Chevy Camaro Z28, Dodge Charger Hellcat, Watkins Glen, Road Racing, motorsport, Formula 1
